# Blockchain Technology & its Applications by Bank of America

## Date: 
28/04/2023

## Event Description:

Do you want to take your knowledge of Fintech to the next level? Get ready to explore the revolutionary world of Blockchain Technology with Bank of America's ‘Blockchain Technology & its Applications’ workshop, hosted by the Department of CSE. As one of the leading banks in the world, Bank of America knows the importance of innovation in financial technology. This workshop will take you on a journey through the fundamentals of Blockchain, including its decentralized and secure nature.

You will learn how this technology can streamline banking processes, reduce costs and increase efficiency, making it a crucial asset to financial institutions worldwide. You'll also dive into the creation and execution of self-executing contracts where the terms of the agreement directly written into lines of code. Register now for Bank of America's ‘Blockchain Technology & its Applications’ workshop and join us in revolutionizing the world of finance!

## Rules and Regulations:

-   Participants are required to bring their own laptops
    
-   No prior knowledge is required
    
-   Participants need not pre-install any software for the workshop
    

## Benefits/Takeaways:

-   The participants will get hands-on experience in learning the basics of blockchain and learn about its applications in the fintech domain.
    
-   The participants will get C20 branded certificates.
    
-   Networking opportunities: Participants will get to network with industry experts and can even get a chance to work on real-life problem statements.
    

## Price: 
Rs.354/-
